---
title: Middle Eastern Beef, Pork & Cauliflower Pie with Veggie Mash Topping
description: You can have anything you want in a pie, it’s totally up to your tastebuds. May we suggest though, this beef and pork version with
Middle Eastern tastes and a variety of oven-roasted veggies. Give this pie a real hit of deliciousness by baking a mix of mashed potato
and carrot on top to make the lid of the pie.

